*Dakle*, oni su se u potpunosti složili. (So, they agreed completely.)

Ona je *dakle* odlučila da to uradi. (So, she decided to do it.)

Ponovo ću *dakle* morati da preispitam svoj stav. (So, I will have to re-examine my stance again.)

*Dakle*, završili smo zadatak. (So, we have finished the task.)

Ona je *dakle* sada u poseti. (So, she is visiting now.)